copy DD-Attendee replacing Attendee by
    ==AttendeeRecord.
    88 EndOfAttendeesFile value high-values==.

fd BackupFile.
copy DD-Attendee replacing Attendee by
    ==BackupRecord.
    88 EndOfBackupFile value high-values==.

